<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12 spacer"></div>

    @*RSVP*@
    <div class="col-lg-12 btn_rsvp_outer" >
            @{Html.RenderAction("_RSVP", "Shared");}
    </div>
    @*SCHEDULE*@
    <div class="col-lg-8 offset-2 sub_sections text-center" >
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 section_title mb-5">
                <h1>Order of Events</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-12 section_row">
                <div class="row h-100">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 mb-2">
                        <img src="~/Content/images/icons/newlyweds.png" alt="Alternate Text" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 m-auto section_col_left">
                        <h1>The Ceremony</h1>
                      
                        <h5>Saturday, April 14th 2018</h5>
                        <h5>2:30pm</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 m-auto section_col_right">
                        <h1>St.Mary Church</h1>
                        <h5>106 Jackson Street</h5>
                        <h5>Fishkill, NY 12524</h5>
                        <p>Come join us in our union. There will be a bagpiper outside of the church as well as some handsome gents in full kilt attire.</p>
                        <a class="btn" href="https://goo.gl/maps/mpe1FpY8UwR2" target="_blank">Map</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12 section_row">
                <div class="row h-100">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 mb-2">
                        <img src="~/Content/images/icons/cake.png" alt="Alternate Text" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 m-auto section_col_left">
                        <h1>Cocktail Hour & Reception</h1>
                        <h5>Saturday, April 14th 2018</h5>
                        <h5>5:30pm - 10:30pm</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 m-auto section_col_right">
                      
                        <h1>The Thayer Hotel</h1>
                        <h5>General Washington Ballroom</h5>
                        <h5>674 Thayer Road</h5>
                        <h5>West Point, NY 10996</h5>
                        <p>A night of dinner, dancing and drinks to celebrate the newly married couple!</p>
                        <a class="btn" href="https://goo.gl/maps/ADQMcCPgrap" target="_blank">Map</a>
                        <a class="btn" href="http://www.thethayerhotel.com/" target="_blank">Visit the Property</a>
                       
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12 section_row">
                <div class="row h-100">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 mb-2">
                        <img src="~/Content/images/icons/champagne.png" alt="Alternate Text" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 m-auto section_col_left">
                        <h1>After Party</h1>
                        <h5>Saturday, April 14th 2018</h5>
                        <h5>10:30pm - 2:00am</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 m-auto section_col_right">
                        <h1>The Thayer Hotel</h1>
                        <h5>Zulu Time Bar</h5>
                       <p>Where the real party starts. This is a rooftop bar located directly above the reception hall. Sure to be a good time! if it is closed we will bring the party to an inside bar</p>
                        <a class="btn" href="https://goo.gl/maps/ADQMcCPgrap" target="_blank">Map</a>
                        <a class="btn" href="http://www.thethayerhotel.com/zulu-time-rooftop-bar-and-lounge.html" target="_blank">Visit the Room</a>
                   
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12 section_row">
                <div class="row h-100">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 mb-2">
                        <img src="~/Content/images/icons/plate.png" alt="Alternate Text" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 m-auto section_col_left">
                        <h1>Brunch</h1>
                        <h5>Sunday, April 15th 2018</h5>
                        <h5>12:00pm - 2:00pm</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 m-auto section_col_right">
                        <h1>The Thayer Hotel</h1>
                        <h5>General Dwight Eisenhower Room</h5>
                        <p>After a night of partying we would hate to let you go hungry! Join us for a brunch the morning after.</p>
                        <a class="btn" href="https://goo.gl/maps/ADQMcCPgrap" target="_blank">Map</a>
                        <a class="btn" href="http://www.thethayerhotel.com/sunday-champagne-brunch.html" target="_blank">Visit the Room</a>
                 
                      
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-12 spacer"></div>
</div>



